list.abstract: Master（英[ˈmɑːstə]，美[ˈmæstər]），英语单词，作名词用，为老爷；主人；主子。作形容词用，为精通的；主要的；技术熟练的。作动词用，为精通；掌握；控制。短语搭配有master plan（总体规划；蓝图），例句为“He asked to see the station master.（他要求见站长。）” Master及物动词类近义词有possess、contain、regulate等，名词类近义词有teacher、professor、artist等，形容词类近义词有experienced、primary、major等。masters为Master的复数形式以及第三人称单数。

Master在斯诺克领域是斯诺克著名赛事——温布利大师赛的名称。该赛事以悠久的历史、极高的国际影响力被誉为斯诺克的三大赛（令两大赛事指英国锦标赛、世界锦标赛）之一。夺得温布利大师赛冠军也是每个顶级球手的理想之一。如果一个球手完成了夺得Master、Uk、WC三大赛冠军的壮举，也就是实现了大满贯，完成了作为职业球员的终极追求。该赛事虽不计积分，但是水平极高，只有世界排名前16的球员加上一名外卡、一名资格赛冠军有资格参加。因此，在master历史上诞生过许多经典的对局。台球皇帝斯蒂芬亨德利曾六度夺冠，是当之无愧的master王中王。以下是master历年决赛的情况：
2010年，大师赛决赛的两名球员依旧是奥沙利文和塞尔比，只不过这次卫冕冠军换成了奥沙利文。最终，塞尔比在6-9落后的局面下顽强追击，凭借超强的心理素质再一次捍卫了逆转王的美誉，连扳四局再次缔造经典，第二次夺得master冠军。

yingyinNormal.en: So he is now your partner, master.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以他现在是您的伙伴了，主人。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my master. Such a brilliant scheme.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，主人，您的计划实在高明。

yingyinNormal.en: Where'd you get it? It belongs to his master.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你从哪搞来的？这是它主人的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Master, it's time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 主人，是时候了。

yingyinNormal.en: We were both raised in a zoo by the same master.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们都在动物园中被同一个主人养大。

yingyinNormal.en: To serve the most despicable master they could find. Boss. Boss.
yingyinNormal.zh: 找到并侍奉这世上最卑鄙的主人。老大，老大。

yingyinNormal.en: Making their master happy was the tribe's very reason for existence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小黄人种族存在的意义就是为了让他们的主人开心。

yingyinNormal.en: Dobby. So this is your master. The family you serve is the Malfoys.
yingyinNormal.zh: 多比。原来他就是你的主人，你服侍的家庭就是马福尔家。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Azog the Defiler was sent to kill them. His master seeks control of the mountain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 毁灭者阿佐格被派去截杀他们，他的主人意图控制那座山。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: Let me speak to him. Master, you are not strong enough. I have strength enough for this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来跟他说。主人，你的体力还不够。我对付这件事体力足够啦。

yingyinNormal.en: Tell your master I will meet him to hear his gracious offerings. Limp away now, messenger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 告诉你的主人，我会去见他听听他慷慨的条款，快跛着出去吧，信使。

yingyinNormal.en: But I mostly use it to help my master sleep. He lies awake at night thinking about his progeny.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我主要用这种能力帮我的主人睡眠。他晚上想着他的后代，难以成眠。

yingyinNormal.en: This, sir? It is a mark of the house-elf's enslavement. Dobby can only be freed if his master presents him with clothes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个吗？这是家庭小精灵的奴隶标志，只有主人送衣服给多比时多比才能自由。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: The dark ages were actually fun times. Their new master had a tendency to party all night and sleep all day. Ahem. Yoo-hoo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 欧洲中世纪其实挺好玩的，他们的新主人有白天睡觉，晚上狂欢的癖好。咳咳，哟呼。

yingyinNormal.en: Master, I just want to assure you that I had no part in this hopeless plan. Preparing a dinner, designing a gown for her, giving her a suite in the east wing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 主人,我只是想向你保证我没参与这悲催的计划。准备晚餐，为她设计礼服，给她一间在东塔的卧室。

yingyinNormal.en: You'll join me for dinner. That's not a request. Gently, Master. The girl lost her father and her freedom in one day. Yes, the poor thing is probably in there, scare to death. Exactly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 过来和我吃饭。我不是在邀请你。温柔点，主人。仅仅一天的时间里她失去了父亲还失去了自由。是啊，可伶的孩子。独自一人肯定吓坏了。就是。

yingyinNormal.en: Master! Master! I have... It's... It's very bad news.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真人 真人，我... 我有个...是个... 是个很坏的消息。

yingyinNormal.en: That is no illusion, Master.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这可不是假像啊，真人。

yingyinNormal.en: Master! Shifu Shifu, are you OK?
yingyinNormal.zh: 大师，石师父！你没事吧?

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Rabbit is the station master.
yingyinNormal.zh: 兔先生是车站管理员。

examination_example.sentence: There are a number of approaches to <highlight>mastering</highlight> the art of deep work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有许多方法可以掌握深度工作的艺术。

examination_example.sentence: The key to <highlight>mastering</highlight> the art of deep work is to keep to your focus time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 掌握深度工作艺术的关键是保持你的专注时间。
